parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to properly repair or replace Takata airbags can lead to serious injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident, as well as inconvenience and frustration for vehicle owners.
symptoms: Airbag warning light illuminated
airbag deployed improperly
airbag inflator ruptured
inability to repair or replace airbags due to part unavailability
delayed or refused repairs by dealerships.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of repair parts for Takata airbag recalls can leave vehicle owners at risk of serious injury or fatality in the event of an accident, as well as cause frustration and inconvenience.
symptoms: Dealerships unable to repair or replace airbags due to part unavailability
delayed or refused repairs
vehicle owners forced to continue driving with potentially faulty airbags.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Delayed or refused repairs by dealerships can leave vehicle owners at risk of serious injury or fatality in the event of an accident, as well as cause frustration and inconvenience.
symptoms: Dealerships refusing to repair or replace airbags
delayed repairs
vehicle owners forced to continue driving with potentially faulty airbags.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive oil consumption can lead to premature engine wear, increased emissions, and potentially cause engine failure, which can result in costly repairs or even accidents.
symptoms: The oil level warning light comes on frequently
the oil level is low
the vehicle is burning oil at an accelerated rate
the oil life is reduced to 40-50% before the warning light comes on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine compartment fires can cause significant damage to the vehicle, potentially leading to engine failure, and pose a risk to the safety of the occupants and other road users.
symptoms: Smoke coming from the engine compartment
burning rubber smell
visible flames from the engine area
heavy smoke coming from the hood.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unexplained shattering of the moonroof glass can cause a loud noise, distraction, and debris to fall into the vehicle, potentially leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Loud explosion or noise
moonroof glass shattering without any apparent cause
glass shards falling into the vehicle
no evidence of external impact or debris.
